If you go to the next slide, there are two QR codes.

26:07.476 --> 26:15.186
One is for the given page of the church and the other is to join a team and serve.

26:17.378 --> 26:19.643
It could also be in the context of a life group.

26:19.963 --> 26:33.511
It could be what you have to give as a time, is a listening ear to someone, is an encouragement, is just to show up and be there for someone who just needs to come to a community of believers.

26:36.196 --> 26:39.122
And these are practical ways.

26:39.266 --> 26:46.995
These are practical next steps to take in our journey of practicing and living a life of generosity.

26:47.035 --> 27:01.831
Yeah, so the other thing I sensed a lot place on my heart as I was preparing for this is, you know that one about giving up all to God, not living a segmented life?

27:02.212 --> 27:03.753
I think that one really stood out for me.

27:03.813 --> 27:08.018
And I think some of us might still

27:08.258 --> 27:13.267
be struggling with trusting God completely.

27:14.308 --> 27:20.119
We're trusting God completely and we will think, man, this thing is gonna collapse.

27:20.159 --> 27:33.682
If I don't keep holding everything, if I'm not in control and maybe God is just saying to you this morning, like, just trust me with this, trust me.

27:35.874 --> 27:37.877
I just want to add one quick thing.

27:37.917 --> 27:43.625
The whole membership thing, the thing with a membership is that you have to pay it.

27:43.645 --> 27:50.514
That's why giving is not a membership.

27:50.534 --> 27:51.816
It's a response to worship.

27:53.678 --> 27:58.925
We give not because we feel obliged or because there's a rule that you have to follow.

27:58.965 --> 28:05.394
We give because the Lord puts on our heart to give.

28:05.538 --> 28:08.802
You know, we don't stand up here inviting people to give.

28:10.804 --> 28:12.507
We invite you to seek the Lord.

28:13.247 --> 28:16.772
We invite you to ask Him what He would have you do with your life.

28:17.192 --> 28:23.420
Well, we seek Him, we invite you to ask Him, Lord, what would you have me give?

28:23.900 --> 28:28.987
Not what would the church have us give, not would David and Nickele or have you give or Palumi.

28:29.567 --> 28:31.229
But Lord, what would you have me give?

28:32.891 --> 28:34.994
How do I start this journey of generosity?

28:37.090 --> 28:42.778
So we don't want anyone to feel like kind of, there's any sort of prerequisite to be in part of this church.

28:43.159 --> 28:44.641
It depends on what you give.

28:45.022 --> 28:47.085
That's not how it works.

28:47.866 --> 28:51.832
The invitation is to respond to Jesus in worship.

28:52.994 --> 28:54.035
It's an act of worship.

28:54.075 --> 28:58.021
And I just feel that is the word that Plumey just used, trust.

28:59.543 --> 29:02.107
I felt that was the word for today.

29:02.127 --> 29:04.010
We have lots of words for today.

29:04.791 --> 29:06.674
And there's a,

29:07.554 --> 29:10.979
In Matthew 6, there's a passage.

29:11.280 --> 29:13.803
I'd really encourage you to go and read the whole thing because we haven't got time to read it.

29:14.344 --> 29:15.105
Do not worry.

29:16.207 --> 29:19.732
It talks about the birds of the air and the flowers of the fields and all of that.

29:20.373 --> 29:22.556
And it has this little line in it, if I can find it.

29:24.840 --> 29:31.690
So do not worry, say, what shall we eat or what shall we drink or what shall we wear for the pagans run after these things.

29:32.211 --> 29:34.514
And your heavenly Father knows that you need them.

29:36.354 --> 29:41.720
Underneath that is actually a promise that the Lord will provide for your needs.

29:43.882 --> 29:46.025
And so the invitation is to trust.

29:48.327 --> 29:52.071
To trust in the one who holds you in his hands.

29:53.653 --> 30:02.002
And so that's where I'd like us to go in ministry is to think, right, do I trust the Lord or have I lived a segmented life?

30:03.298 --> 30:07.665
Am I sort of holding on to parts because I just can't let him take control?

30:09.788 --> 30:11.931
So should we just pray into that?

30:11.951 --> 30:14.915
And truth be known, none of us are perfect.

30:17.339 --> 30:26.172
Whether it's our finances, our time, our energy, our relationships, there's going to be areas that we need to hand over to the Lord.

30:26.212 --> 30:28.516
So Lord, we just invite you to come.

30:28.596 --> 30:29.938
Holy Spirit, just come.

